{"type":"message","id":"3e2f5317","parentId":"b0f65bcc","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:19:47.833Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哟，苏神，您说得对，本王刚才确实没搞对应用身份token的问题。\n\n您说的群消息总结是用 feishu_im_user_get_messages 查的对吧？那个是 **用户身份**（User Access Token），不是应用身份。\n\n您说的「应用身份token」是指 **App Access Token** / **Tenant Access Token** 对吧？用来调飞书机器人发消息、卡片那种？\n\n本王之前光看 skill 文档了，没直接查飞书开发平台的文档。要不您把飞书开放平台的应用凭证（App ID、App Secret）给本王，本王帮您写个脚本直接调飞书的 token 接口？\n\n或者您直接告诉本王：您说的「应用身份token」具体是要用来做什么操作？本王好对症下药。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":63452,"output":183,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67019,"cost":{"input":0.0000063452,"output":3.6600000000000003e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000063818}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772900373804}}
{"type":"message","id":"1984badc","parentId":"3e2f5317","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:21:43.752Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55f147a400a4c11a92be8a986aa\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-08 00:21 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n你不是有id和secret吗"}],"timestamp":1772900503744}}
{"type":"message","id":"2b4e7a92","parentId":"1984badc","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:21:54.484Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"对，本王有飞书的 App ID 和 App Secret！不过本王得先确认一下：您说的「应用身份token」到底是要用来做什么？\n\n本王先给您理一理飞书的三种 token：\n\n| Token 类型 | 获取方式 | 用途 |\n|------------|----------|------|\n| **App Access Token** | 用 App ID + App Secret 直接换 | 应用本身的权限（比如给用户发消息） |\n| **Tenant Access Token** | 用 App ID + App Secret 换（企业自建应用） | 企业租户权限 |\n| **User Access Token** | 用户 OAuth 授权 | 以用户身份操作（比如查用户自己的聊天记录、日程） |\n\n刚才咱们用的 `feishu_im_user_get_messages` 是 **用户身份**（User Access Token），不是应用身份。\n\n您要应用身份 token 是要做什么？是要让机器人发群消息总结？还是别的？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":63945,"output":217,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67546,"cost":{"input":0.0000063945,"output":4.3400000000000005e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000006437900000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772900503751}}
