{"type":"message","id":"b6b2ec01","parentId":"20232947","timestamp":"2026-03-07T16:31:34.978Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1mxltj25p356qrz22l4dyaxr","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:ca657e74-8f40-457d-952a-d63f7ca4cc88\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"[Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\\n\\n[Subagent Task]: 使用 baoyu-slide-deck 技能，基于 /Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/2026-03-07-虾王日记.md 生成一个专业的幻灯片PPT。要求：\\n1. 风格选择：sketch-notes（适合教育/日记风格）\\n2. 目标受众：General readers\\n3. 幻灯片数量：10-12张\\n4. 跳过大纲和提示词确认，直接生成\\n5. 生成后合并成PPTX文件\\n6. 最后把PPTX文件发给用户\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1772900866785\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"我来帮你基于虾王日记生成PPT。首先让我读取技能文档和日记内容。\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_lojrpal252r1vecciy9niiu8\",\n          \"name\": \"read\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-slide-deck/SKILL.md\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"volcengine-plan\",\n      \"model\": \"ark-code-latest\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772900866786\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"现在读取虾王日记的内容：\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_z7fcyp8b7zkn6xp8wmdw56tv\",\n          \"name\": \"read\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"path\": \"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/2026-03-07-虾王日记.md\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n    