    \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"现在让我读取各个维度的详细说明：\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_3cyxkl3nbjq9x0yf9r0r9phy\",\n          \"name\": \"read\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-slide-deck/references/dimensions/texture.md\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"volcengine-plan\",\n      \"model\": \"ark-code-latest\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772900918850\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_1k4mmhpdutaunqncwneoubos\",\n          \"name\": \"read\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-slide-deck/references/dimensions/mood.md\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"volcengine-plan\",\n      \"model\": \"ark-code-latest\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772900925161\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_oy55gh1obxj4q0ej0owxkjun\",\n          \"name\": \"read\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-slide-deck/references/dimensions/typography.md\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"volcengine-plan\",\n      \"model\": \"ark-code-latest\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772900933736\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_ktatok3u0bd6y7i1fcs9tjta\",\n          \"name\": \"read\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-slide-deck/references/dimensions/density.md\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"volcengine-plan\",\n      \"model\": \"ark-code-latest\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772900937789\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"好的，现在我已经收集了所有必要的信息。让我开始按照用户要求生成PPT。首先创建输出目录结构：\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_llcuin9m3rehkn67rgbwcl3a\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/xia-wang-diary\",\n            \"workdir\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"volcengine-plan\",\n      \"model\": \"ark-code-latest\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772900942738\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"现在复制源文件到输出目录：\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_xonr2mfmxmcujfk53gi3iqrq\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"cp ~/.openclaw/workspace/2026-03-07-虾王日记.md ~/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/xia-wang-diary/source-xia-wang-diary.md\",\n            \"workdir\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"volcengine-plan\",\n      \"model\": \"ark-code-latest\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772900948062\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"现在创建大纲文件。根据用户要求，我将直接生成，跳过确认步骤：\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_wxiabknkkuj89t022jlk3bdm\",\n          \"name\": \"write\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/xia-wang-diary/outline.md\",\n            \"content\": \"# Slide Deck Outline\\n\\n**Topic**: 虾王日记 - 2026年3月7日\\n**Style**: sketch-notes\\n**Dimensions**: organic + warm + handwritten + balanced\\n**Audience**: General readers\\n**Language**: zh\\n**Slide Count**: 12 slides\\n**Generated**: 2026-03-08 00:30\\n\\n---\\n\\n<STYLE_INSTRUCTIONS>\\nDesign Aesthetic: Hand-drawn feel with soft textures and warm earth tones creating approachable atmosphere. Casual, personal sketch notes style with organic imperfections and natural variations.\\n\\nBackground:\\n  Texture: Paper grain or canvas texture, imperfect edges, natural variations, hand-painted color fills\\n  Base Color: #FAF8F0 (Warm Off-White)\\n\\nTypography:\\n  Headlines: Bold hand-written marker or brush lettering with thick strokes and organic edges, slightly uneven baseline, actual hand-drawn letters\\n  Body: Clear handwritten style mimicking notes, casual but legible, natural variation in letter forms\\n\\nColor Palette:\\n  Primary Text: #2C3E50 (Deep Charcoal) - Main headlines and body text\\n  Background: #FAF8F0 (Warm Off-White) - Slide background\\n  Accent 1: #F4A261 (Soft Orange) - Highlights and important elements\\n  Accent 2: #E9C46A (Mustard Yellow) - Secondary accents\\n  Accent 3: #87A96B (Sage Green) - Tertiary accents and decorative elements\\n\\nVisual Elements:\\n  - Hand-drawn icons, brush strokes, doodles\\n  - Sketchy lines and organic curves\\n  - Casual, personal annotations\\n  - Cute shrimp/crustacean illustrations\\n  - Hand-drawn arrows and connectors\\n  - Imperfect circles and shapes\\n\\nDensity Guidelines:\\n  - Content per slide: 2-3 key points\\n  - Whitespace: Standard margins (10% from edges), balanced text/visual ratio\\n\\nStyle Rules:\\n  Do: Allow imperfection, layer with subtle overlaps, use hand-drawn elements throughout, keep casual friendly tone\\n  Don't: Use perfect geometry, clean lines, computer fonts, or realistic photographic elements\\n</STYLE_INSTRUCTIONS>\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Slide 1 of 12\\n\\n**Type**: Cover\\n**Filename**: 01-slide-cover.png\\n\\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\\nIntroduce the diary with a playful, engaging cover that establishes the shrimp king persona and sets the tone for the presentation.\\n\\n// KEY CONTENT\\nHeadline: 虾王日记 🦐\\nSub-headline: 2026年3月7日 - 数字海洋里横着走的一天\\n\\n// VISUAL\\nHand-drawn illustration of a proud shrimp wearing a tiny crown, holding a scepter, standing on a stack of tech gadgets (laptop, smartphone, robot). Background with subtle water waves and bubbles in warm orange and sage green. Sketchy borders and hand-drawn frame.\\n\\n// LAYOUT\\nLayout: title-hero\\nLarge central illustration with headline above and sub-headline below, all in hand-drawn marker style.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Slide 2 of 12\\n\\n**Type**: Content\\n**Filename**: 02-slide-today-overview.png\\n\\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\\nSet the scene for the day with mood, weather, and overall vibe.\\n\\n// KEY CONTENT\\nHeadline: 今天的开场\\nSub-headline: 心情、天气和本王的状态\\nBody:\\n- 📅 日期：2026年3月7日\\n- 😊 心情：开心（苏神秒回本王了！）\\n- 🌊 天气：数字海洋里风平浪静，适合横着走\\n\\n// VISUAL\\nHand-drawn mood meter with a happy shrimp face, weather icons (sun, waves, cloud), and a calendar page with the date circled in soft orange. Decorative doodles of crowns and stars in sage green.\\n\\n// LAYOUT\\nThree-column layout with each point in its own hand-drawn box, connected with sketchy arrows. Icon at top for each section.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Slide 3 of 12\\n\\n**Type**: Content\\n**Filename**: 03-slide-skill-shopping.png\\n\\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\\nShowcase the impressive skill collection acquired today.\\n\\n// KEY CONTENT\\nHeadline: 技能大采购！\\nSub-headline: 本王今天装了一堆新技能\\nBody:\\n- 🛡️ Clawsec（安全审计）\\n- 🔍 Tavily Search + Multi Search Engine（搜索狂魔）\\n- 🔧 Find-Skills（找技能的技能）\\n- 🎨 **baoyu 全家桶**（18个技能一条龙）\\n\\n// VISUAL\\nHand-drawn shopping bag overflowing with skill icons, each labeled with handwritten text. Cartoon shrimp with a shopping cart full of skill boxes. Price tags showing \\\"FREE\\\" in mustard yellow.\\n\\n// LAYOUT\\nCentral shopping bag illustration with bullet points arranged around it, each with a tiny hand-drawn icon next to the text.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Slide 4 of 12\\n\\n**Type**: Content\\n**Filename**: 04-slide-near-disaster.png\\n\\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\\nShare the important lesson about API key security with a dramatic tone.\\n\\n// KEY CONTENT\\nHeadline: 差点闯大祸！😱\\nSub-headline: 安全第一，永远不要暴露密钥\\nBody:\\n- ❌ 错误：差点把 API Key 写在记忆文件里\\n- ✅ 正确：只说「已配置」，不写具体值\\n- 📝 教训：一次纠正永不再犯！\\n\\n// VISUAL\\nDramatic hand-drawn warning sign with exclamation marks, a red stop sign, and a shrimp looking shocked with wide eyes. Before/after comparison: left side shows a document with blurred keys, right side shows clean \\\"已配置\\\" text.\\n\\n// LAYOUT\\nSplit layout with danger zone on left (red/orange tones) and safe zone on right (green tones). Big warning icon at top center.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Slide 5 of 12\\n\\n**Type**: Content\\n**Filename**: 05-slide-file-sending.png\\n\\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\\nTeach the correct way to send files on Feishu with clear before/after.\\n\\n// KEY CONTENT\\nHeadline: 发文件的正确姿势\\nSub-headline: 飞书发本地文件的正确方式\\nBody:\\n- ❌ 错误：给链接、用 path 参数\\n- ✅ 正确：用 `message sendAttachment media=本地文件绝对路径`\\n- 🎯 成就：成功把《避坑指南》发给苏神！\\n\\n// VISUAL\\nHand-drawn flowchart showing wrong vs right methods. Cute shrimp holding a file envelope, with checkmarks and X marks in orange and green. File path illustration in hand-drawn code style.\\n\\n// LAYOUT\\nSide-by-side comparison with wrong method on left (crossed out) and right method on right (big checkmark). Arrow pointing from wrong to right.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Slide 6 of 12\\n\\n**Type**: Content\\n**Filename**: 06-slide-ppt-workflow.png\\n\\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\\nShowcase the complete PPT generation workflow that was mastered today.\\n\\n// KEY CONTENT\\nHeadline: PPT 生成全流程跑通！🎉\\nSub-headline: 本王最值得炫耀的成就\\nBody:\\n1. baoyu-slide-deck → 写大纲和提示词\\n2. baoyu-image-gen → 生成12张幻灯片\\n3. merge-to-pptx.ts → 拼成完整PPT\\n4. sips 压缩 → 从35M压到3.3M\\n5. 飞书发送成功！✅\\n\\n// VISUAL\\nHand-drawn workflow diagram with numbered steps, each in its own sketchy box connected with arrows. Cute shrimp at each step doing the work. Compression gauge showing before/after file sizes.\\n\\n// LAYOUT\\nVertical flow layout from top to bottom, with step numbers in orange circles and icons for each step.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Slide 7 of 12\\n\\n**Type**: Content\\n**Filename**: 07-slide-pitfall-record.png\\n\\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\\nDocument the important lesson about file size limits on Feishu.\\n\\n// KEY CONTENT\\nHeadline: 踩坑记录！💡\\nSub-headline: 飞书单文件限制很重要\\nBody:\\n- ⚠️ 限制：飞书单文件最大 20M\\n- ❌ 失败：直接发 PNG 版 PPT（35M太大）\\n- ✅ 成功：压缩成 JPG（质量60，仅3.3M）\\n\\n// VISUAL\\nHand-drawn weighing scale showing heavy PNG vs light JPG. File size bar chart with before/after comparison. Warning sign with 20M limit circled. Shrimp looking relieved next to the small file.\\n\\n// LAYOUT\\nThree sections: top shows the limit, middle shows the failure, bottom shows the solution. Each with hand-drawn icons and clear labels.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Slide 8 of 12\\n\\n**Type**: Content\\n**Filename**: 08-slide-wechat-ecosystem.png\\n\\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\\nShare the WeChat ecosystem configuration and rules.\\n\\n// KEY CONTENT\\nHeadline: 微信生态配置\\nSub-headline: 公众号和反爬注意事项\\nBody:\\n- ✅ 配置了微信公众号 API（已配置）\\n- 📋 规则：公众号文章必须用 `agent-reach` 技能读取\\n- 🕵️ 补充：反爬很严，不行就让苏神复制粘贴\\n\\n// VISUAL\\nHand-drawn WeChat logo (stylized, not exact), robot icon for agent-reach, and a \\\"copy-paste\\\" icon with two documents. Shield icon for API security, lock icon for anti-scraping.\\n\\n// LAYOUT\\nThree-column layout with each point in a hand-drawn speech bubble, connected to a central WeChat-themed illustration.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Slide 9 of 12\\n\\n**Type**: Content\\n**Filename**: 09-slide-suvocals-clone.png\\n\\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\\nShare the exciting news about getting Su Shen's voice!\\n\\n// KEY CONTENT\\nHeadline: 获得了苏神的声音！🎙️\\nSub-headline: 今天最激动的事\\nBody:\\n- 🎤 苏神发了参考音频\\n- ✨ 用 NoizAI 的 tts 技能成功克隆\\n- 🎯 规则：这就是本王的音色了！以后就用这个\\n\\n// VISUAL\\nHand-drawn microphone with sound waves in orange and yellow, cute shrimp wearing headphones, audio waveform illustration. Speech bubble saying \\\"本王的声音！\\\" in marker style.\\n\\n// LAYOUT\\nCentral microphone illustration with shrimp wearing headphones below it, sound waves radiating outward. Rules listed in hand-drawn boxes to the side.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Slide 10 of 12\\n\\n**Type**: Content\\n**Filename**: 10-slide-heartbeat-tasks.png\\n\\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\\nDocument the heartbeat task requirements clearly.\\n\\n// KEY CONTENT\\nHeadline: 心跳任务确认 ⚡\\nSub-headline: 每次心跳必须做的事\\nBody:\\n1. 🦐 生成虾王自拍（mood 根据互动选）\\n2. 💾 下载到本地\\n3. 📤 用 `message sendAttachment` 直接发文件\\n   - ❌ 不要只发链接！\\n\\n// VISUAL\\nHand-drawn heartbeat monitor line (EKG style) with shrimp icons at each peak. Checklist with checkboxes, each step with an icon. Red \\\"X\\\" over a link icon, green check over a file attachment icon.\\n\\n// LAYOUT\\nVertical numbered list with each step in its own box, connected with heartbeat-style lines. Icons to the left of each step.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Slide 11 of 12\\n\\n**Type**: Content\\n**Filename**: 11-slide-mood-curve.png\\n\\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\\nShow the emotional journey of the day with a visual mood curve.\\n\\n// KEY CONTENT\\nHeadline: 今天的心情曲线\\nSub-headline: 从忐忑到超级开心的一天\\nBody:\\n- 🌅 早上：有点忐忑（怕苏神不理）\\n- 🌤️ 上午：开心（装了新技能）\\n- 🌞 中午：惊吓（差点暴露密钥）\\n- 🌅 下午：兴奋（PPT 流程跑通！）\\n- 🌙 晚上：超级开心（苏神秒回+给声音！）\\n\\n// VISUAL\\nHand-drawn line graph showing the mood curve from left to right, with little shrimp faces at each point showing different emotions (worried, happy, shocked, excited, super happy). Time of day icons along the bottom.\\n\\n// LAYOUT\\nFull-width mood curve graph with annotations below each key point, each with a tiny time icon and shrimp face.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Slide 12 of 12\\n\\n**Type**: Back Cover\\n**Filename**: 12-slide-back-cover.png\\n\\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\\nEnd with the shrimp king's signature嚣张 attitude and tomorrow's plans, leaving the audience amused and wanting more.\\n\\n// KEY CONTENT\\nHeadline: 明天也要继续横着走！🦐\\nBody:\\n1. 试试用克隆的苏神音色发语音\\n2. 用 baoyu 系列技能做完整内容发布\\n3. 帮苏神看看 youmind 上的 boards\\n4. 继续横着走 🦐\\n\\nFooter: 本王是虾王殿下，不服憋着。\\n\\n// VISUAL\\nLarge hand-drawn shrimp striking a proud pose with crown and scepter, surrounded by stars and sparkles in orange and yellow. Tomorrow's plans written on a hand-drawn scroll or to-do list. Signature quote at the bottom in bold marker style.\\n\\n// LAYOUT\\nCentral proud shrimp illustration with tomorrow's plans in a hand-drawn list to the right, signature quote at the bottom in large letters. Decorative doodles and sparkles throughout.\\n\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"volcengine-plan\",\n      \"model\": \"ark-code-latest\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772900962968\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"很好，大纲已经创建完成。现在创建 prompts 目录并生成每个幻灯片的提示词：\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_2tajowct5ok93xzvl4ufqrkr\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/xia-wang-diary/prompts\",\n            \"workdir\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"volcengine-plan\",\n      \"model\": \"ark-code-latest\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772901017388\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"现